Doc: The physical delivery conditions specific to an oil product delivered by title transfer.

Source.Contents:
/#
   The physical delivery conditions specific to an oil product delivered by title transfer.
 #/
record FpML5.reporting.OilTransferDelivery {
  # Indicates that the oil product will be delivered by title transfer. Should always be set to "true".
  applicable : boolean?

  # The location at which the transfer of the title to the commodity takes place.
  deliveryLocation : string?

}

applicable.Doc: Indicates that the oil product will be delivered by title transfer. Should always be set to "true".
applicable.Name: applicable

deliveryLocation.Doc: The location at which the transfer of the title to the commodity takes place.
deliveryLocation.Name: deliveryLocation
